description:
Well, the time has finally come. The Acolyte is here, and its time to talk about it. So join me, MauLer, Star Wars Theory, Robot Head, Echo Chamberlain and Chris Gore as we review the first two episodes, and Chris spills the beans on THAT Episode 3. 

Subscribe to Star Wars Theory: https://www.youtube.com/@StarWarsTheory
Subscribe to Robot Head: https://www.youtube.com/@RobotHead
Subscribe to Echo: https://www.youtube.com/@EchoChamberlain
Subscribe to Film Threat: https://www.youtube.com/@FilmThreat
title: Open Bar #98 - The Acolyte Is Upon Us, Movie Theatres Dying, Can Anything Save Hollywood?

description: Just when you thought Star Wars was dead, along comes a show like The Acolyte and totally proves you right. Join me for my review of Episode 1 of Leslye Headland's Star Wars "masterpiece".
title: The Acolyte Episode 1 - A Stunning And Brave Disaster
